  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>PROJECT HUNT is a hunting game for players who enjoy tracking animals and taking precise shots without dealing with a wall of hardcore sim mechanics.</strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Follow tracks, read the wind, set up your shot, and then review exactly where your bullets hit on detailed animal models.</strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>The focus is on satisfying gunplay and exciting animal encounters rather than ultra-realistic ballistics or complex gear management.</strong> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2451010/extras/b83b391d3c98a013171c530f88aa4189.avif?t=1767365514\" width=616 height=346 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2451010/extras/e4c2871f0d577dedae8491f084504a95.avif?t=1767365514\" width=616 height=346 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2451010/extras/9ee0fc4693493539e6868070ad1df8eb.avif?t=1767365514\" width=616 height=384 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2451010/extras/51c694601ff06bc9195dadadb5ab04c8.avif?t=1767365514\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2451010/extras_big/51c694601ff06bc9195dadadb5ab04c8.avif?t=1767365514 width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2451010/extras/c11ca7addd3289080689fa41c2d40d81.avif?t=1767365514\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2451010/extras_bi